data.description: This stunning 3-bed, 2-full bath, 2-half bath home on .54 acres is a private paradise. Newly painted and carpeted, it boasts an in-ground saltwater pool with new liner and pump, alongside an outdoor shower hose for convenience. The crawlspace is meticulously maintained with moisture control and sensors. Embrace the privacy of the fenced backyard, while the screened porch allows for moments of relaxation. The garage conversion, complete with a half bath and plumbing, offers versatile living options—perfect for an in-law suite, game room, or a personalized business space. Entertain effortlessly with a fire pit, ideal for cozy gatherings under the stars. A storage unit with power adds practicality to the property. With a master on the main floor, this home is a seamless blend of comfort and functionality, offering a private haven with endless possibilities.
